event.title: FOSDEM '25 - Funding the FOSS Ecosystem in Brussels, Belgium

body.p: The FSFE is co-organizing this debuting that wants to bring together developers, maintainers, policymakers, entrepreneurs, donors and funders to explore various getting paid models and mechanisms that ensure the longevity and security of FOSS projects.
FOSDEM 2025 is taking place on 1 and 2 February at the ULB Solbosch Campus, Brussels
